title: Dean Koontz - Odd Thomas series - epub complete
description:
Odd Thomas is a series of thriller novels by prolific American author Dean Koontz featuring the title character. Odd Thomas is a twenty year-old fry cook and talented writer from California who can converse with the dead.

Dean Koontz began the Odd Thomas book series in 2003 with the title novel, Odd Thomas, and wrapped it up with 'Saint Odd' in 2015. The series is currently being adapted into a feature film by director Stephen Summers
